N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 645-4.16 - Consistency with other laws

State Regulations

Nothing herein is intended to limit the rights of any
party in an enforcement proceeding pursuant to the ECL. The statutory
provisions of the ECL and the State Administrative Procedure Act shall control
over an inconsistent provision in this Subpart. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
645-4.16

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
